    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at or above required levels for MRL 5 Class III device. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification comprehensively propagates input variability across all uncertain parameters; 95th percentile hemolysis index predictions remain below the absolute clinical threshold with margin. Validation activities conducted on the target geometry across the full COU operating envelope. Discretization error bounded by GCI analysis. Independent use-error review completed. Package meets all credibility requirements for submission.",
